{
  "stem": "2804.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we walked-- when we went into it, we went in with some of the GIs and the doctors, we were even told not to look too much, because they have found some of the Germans had mixed in with the people.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- they knew who they were, and all of a sudden, we saw somebody hanging, you know, from a hook or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We walked in some-- there were different buildings there that we walked into.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the stench was-- I'll never forget the smell of these buildings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were planks, three stories, if you want to-- three levels, which were like skeletons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You found the living, the half-living, and the dead among them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We walked-- we saw a building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we went in, found it was a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was still filled with bodies that they had burned up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the outside were piles and piles of bones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw a building there where they gave them a cake of soap, stripped them, told them to take a shower, and they turned on the gas, the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was another building where there were women and children, women lying on the floor close together, babies, children that looked like they were 50 years old, with the bloated tummies from starvation.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was-- it was a horrible, horrible sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few of us that we went, started to walk through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was-- at the time, when we came out of there and we went into this hotel-like building that was going to be our headquarters, because the army had just been through, and there were still some German officers there that were dead on the floor the GIs took out.",
      "word_count": 55
    }
  ],
